nced a 12-year partnership with Saudi Arabia to host the first-ever Olympic Esports Games.\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 517, \"end\": 554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 602, \"end\": 608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"score\": 0.9999999945321179, \"rank\": 5.4675596735872065e-09, \"text\": \"Arabia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 12-year partnership\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"the first-ever Olympic Esports Games\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's right.\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 668, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Competitive gaming is becoming a staple part of the Olympic program.\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Competitive gaming\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"a staple part\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic program\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With hosts Saudi Arabia issuing an open invitation for countries to compete, can Ireland seize this new opportunity for Olympic glory?\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 873, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 756, \"end\": 762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"score\": 0.9999999945321179, \"rank\": 5.4675596735872065e-09, \"text\": \"Arabia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\"}, {\"begin\": 820, \"end\"