o\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"an unstoppable, global phenomenon\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Across a huge variety of genres, games attract millions of spectators from across the world.\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1161, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a huge variety\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1090}, {\"ngram\": \"genres\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1100}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1107}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1124}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Events easily fill the biggest stadiums for consecutive days.\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Events\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest stadiums\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"consecutive days\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Competitions promise exciting storylines, dramatic rivalries, and shock upsets as any other 'traditional' sport can deliver.\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Competitions\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"exciting storylines\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"dramatic rivalries\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"shock upsets\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"any other 'traditional' sport\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kurt Pittman is the founder and CEO of Dublin esports organisation Nativz Gaming.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1389, \"end\": 1395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"score\": 0.9999970966997662, \"rank\": 2.903194607279835e-06, \"text\": \"Dublin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kurt Pittman\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1362}, {\"ngram\": \"the founder\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"CEO\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Working with New Zealand Rugby League, Fulham FC, Shamrock Rovers, and Shelbourne FC, he has a unique perspective on the crossover between the physical and the virtual state of sports.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_Rugby_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"New Zealand Rugby League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_Rugby_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_Rugby_League\"}, {\"begin\": 1471, \"end\": 1480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fulham_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fulham FC\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fulham_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fulham_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1482, \"end\": 1497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shamrock_Rovers_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.368048024940454e-23, \"text\": \"Shamrock Rovers\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shamrock_Rovers_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shamrock_Rovers_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1503, \"end\": 1516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelbourne_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.746167390146378e-50, \"text\": \"Shelbourne FC\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelbourne_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelbourne_F.C.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a unique perspective\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1545}, {\"ngram\": \"the crossover\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"the virtual state\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Comparing sports and esports from an athlete perspective is not as far-fetched as some may think,\\\" Kurt says.\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1728, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1635}, {\"ngram\": \"esports\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete perspective\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"Kurt\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Esports teams need to analyse opponents' team selections and game plans.\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1803, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Esports teams\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"opponents' team selections\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"game plans\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tasks are undertaken by coaches and analysts.\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tasks\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1809}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1835}, {\"ngram\": \"analysts\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Players are challenged with decision-making under pressure.\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1909, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Players\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1857}, {\"ngram\": \"decision-making\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In team situations, they have to trust their teammates.\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1965, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"team situations\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"their teammates\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Personally, their hand speed and hand-eye coordination are exceptional, and stamina to perform under pressure is essential.\\\"\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 2090, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their hand speed\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"hand-eye coordination\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"stamina\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We need your consent to load this rte-player contentWe use rte-player to manage extra content that can set cookies on your device and collect data about your activity.\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your consent\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2112}, {\"ngram\": \"this rte-player contentWe\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"rte-player\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"extra content\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2185}, {\"ngram\": \"cookies\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2206}, {\"ngram\": \"your device\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"data\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"your activity\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please review their details and accept them to load the content.Manage Preferences At the highest level, esports clubs will have all the resources and support traditional clubs would have.\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2449, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their details\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2287}, {\"ngram\": \"the content\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2323}, {\"ngram\": \"Preferences\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2342}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest level\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"esports clubs\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"all the resources\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"traditional clubs\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This includes access to nutritionists, sports psychologists, physiotherapists, and more.\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2470}, {\"ngram\": \"nutritionists\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"sports psychologists\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2509}, {\"ngram\": \"physiotherapists\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are considered elite athletes in every sense.\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2589, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"elite athletes\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2573}, {\"ngram\": \"every sense\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, navigating the industry can be difficult, especially for newcomers, as Kurt says that the pathways in esports \\\"are not clear.\\\"\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2726, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the industry\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2623}, {\"ngram\": \"newcomers\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2666}, {\"ngram\": \"Kurt\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2675}, {\"ngram\": \"the pathways\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2698}, {\"ngram\": \"esports\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Early involvement in the scene can rely on the passion and dedication of communities to attract attention.\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Early involvement\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2744}, {\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2757}, {\"ngram\": \"the passion\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2781}, {\"ngram\": \"dedication\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"communities\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2811}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Nativz Gaming hopes to change this.\", \"from\": 2835, \"to\": 2874, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nativz Gaming\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 2852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two initiatives, including the growing Irish Esports Collegiate series and a brand new talent academy, aim to nurture talent and help players recognise a clear 'path to pro'.\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 3049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2914, \"end\": 2919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999980770781193, \"rank\": 1.9197321947826416e-06, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2920, \"end\": 2927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6778486692802675e-57, \"text\": \"Esports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Two initiatives\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2890}, {\"ngram\": \"a brand new talent academy\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2976}, {\"ngram\": \"talent\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 2999}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3016}, {\"ngram\": \"a clear 'path\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Historically, collegiate esports has sat on the periphery of the student experience,\\\" Kurt says.\", \"from\": 3051, \"to\": 3148, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"collegiate esports\", \"from\": 3066, \"to\": 3084}, {\"ngram\": \"the periphery\", \"from\": 3096, \"to\": 3109}, {\"ngram\": \"the student experience\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3135}, {\"ngram\": \"Kurt\", \"from\": 3138, \"to\": 3142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The relationship has traditionally been between the organisers and the computer science and engineering societies, with only a few dedicated esports societies.\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The relationship\", \"from\": 3150, \"to\": 3166}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisers\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3212}, {\"ngram\": \"the computer science and engineering societies\", \"from\": 3217, \"to\": 3263}, {\"ngram\": \"only a few dedicated esports societies\", \"from\": 3270, \"to\": 3308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Esports clubs have not emerged yet.\\\"\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3346, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Esports clubs\", \"fro